# Risotto by Amanda

![Risotto](https://www.thespruceeats.com/thmb/5mExmaXLqLawTKT7s34NK3xVOzg=/960x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(webp)/risotto-recipe-for-beginners-996008-hero-01-9ca07ec80a024c80909e0c8a92f0674c.jpg)

## Ingredients
- 1 Tbsp. salt, plus more
- 6 Tbsp. extra-virgin olive oil
- ½ large white onnion, finely chopped (about 1½ cups)
- 2 cups avorio
- 1 cup dry white wine
- 3 cups of vegetable stock
- 5 Tbsp. butter
- 1¾ cups Parmesan
- Black pepper
- Timjan

## Preparation
Chop and fry onions in olive oil

Add rice, let fry for a few minutes

Add white wine and boil down

Add a little stock at a time, and let boil down. Stir frequently

Add butter, grated parmesan and pepper before serving

